The Middelburg Hawks Serious Commercial Crime Investigating Unit arrested him on charges of fraud and money laundering. Lucy Dineo Sekgotodi from the Hawks, said Mr Makua and his co-accused Annica van Staden, are being accused of selling RDP houses without owners’ consent. Also read: Annica van Staden bly in aanhouding sê hof Mr Makua and Miss Van Staden will appear in court on May 11 for a formal bail application. They are both currently in custody. 